    Remove checked-in Go vendor; split flake-check hooks from Go graph hooks

    No symlink and no committed vendor: modules resolve from the network or the
    local cache. nix flake check stays sandboxed without govet/golangci/searchbench-
    architecture; full Go hooks remain in nix develop and pre-push.

